OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,FCampaigners in the Scottish Borders
OL,7,Fhave successfully rallied together to
OL,8,Fbuy the derelict studio of world-
OL,9,Ffamous textile designer Bernat Klein.
OL,11,FA coalition group secured the building
OL,12,Ffor #279,000 at auction with the hope
OL,13,Fof creating a new venue to inspire
OL,14,Fcreatives.
