OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,FBuilt by architect Peter Womersley in
OL,7,F1972, the studio is seen as one of
OL,8,FScotland's most unique 20th-century
OL,9,Fbuildings and was previously a major
OL,10,Fpart of the textile industry. The
OL,11,Fproperty is located north of Selkirk
OL,12,Fnear the A707.
OL,14,FProfessor Alison Harley, Chair of
OL,15,FTrustees, Bernat Klein Foundation,
OL,16,Fbelieves the studio's future "looks
OL,17,Fvery bright".
