OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,FHe said: "We would like to thank
OL,7,Feveryone who has supported our efforts
OL,8,Fso far and we look forward to sharing
OL,9,Fplans and progress over the months
OL,10,Fahead."
OL,12,FThe restoration process is expected to
OL,13,Fcost up to #3 million after more than
OL,14,F20 years on Scotland's Buildings at
OL,15,FRisk Register.
OL,17,FA building assessment from two years
OL,18,Fago identified issues such as water
OL,19,Fdamage, deterioration and acts of
OL,20,Fvandalism.
