OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,FScottish Historic Buildings Trust will
OL,7,Fwork in partnership with the National
OL,8,FTrust for Scotland to complete the
OL,9,Frestoration project.
OL,11,FDr Samuel Gallacher, Director,
OL,12,FScottish Historic Buildings Trust,
OL,13,Fsays the repairs "will take many
OL,14,Fmonths".
