OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,FHe added: "The scale of the repair and
OL,7,Frestoration required at Peter
OL,8,FWomersley's Bernat Klein Studio is
OL,9,Fextensive and will take many months,
OL,10,Fthe skills of specialists and the
OL,11,Fsupport of the many people who have an
OL,12,Finterest in both Peter Womersley and
OL,13,FBernat Klein's work."
OL,15,FCampaigners were able to take over the
OL,16,Fstudio after fundraising more than
OL,17,F#33,000. Financial contributions were
OL,18,Falso provided by The National Trust
OL,19,Ffor Scotland, private organisations
OL,20,Fand people.
