OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,FPhilip Long OBE, Chief Executive,
OL,7,FNational Trust for Scotland, said:
OL,8,F"The Trust along with many others, for
OL,9,Fmany years, have been working behind
OL,10,Fthe scenes to save this outstanding
OL,11,Fmodern building, so important both for
OL,12,Fits architectural design and the rich
OL,13,Fheritage it represents as part of
OL,14,FScotland's world-renowned creativity
OL,15,Fin textiles.
