OL,3,CCampaigners buy the derelict studio of
OL,4,Cfamous designer Bernat Klein
OL,6,F"Now through our partnership, we can
OL,7,Fbe confident this significant
OL,8,Fbuilding, the story of its architect
OL,9,Fand its resident will survive to be
OL,10,Fshared with people now and in the
OL,11,Ffuture and help to inspire new
OL,12,Fcreativity. The National Trust for
OL,13,FScotland is very proud indeed to have
OL,14,Fcontributed to today's wonderful news."
